msgctxt "72_Homeless Man"
msgid "Whoa, Kiryu-san! Never thought I'd run into ya down here.\\r\n"\n"Didn't even realize you were back in town!"
msgstr "¡Vaya, Kiryu-san! Nunca pensé que me encontraría contigo aquí abajo.\\r\n"\n"¡Ni siquiera sabía que estabas de vuelta en la ciudad!"

msgctxt "84_Kiryu"
msgid "Do I know you?"
msgstr "¿Lo conozco?"

msgctxt "96_Homeless Man"
msgid "Heh. Much as you know any old homeless guy, I guess."
msgstr "Heh. Much as you know any old homeless guy, I guess."

msgctxt "108_Homeless Man"
msgid "I know you, though. Owe you a lot, in fact."
msgstr "I know you, though. Owe you a lot, in fact."

msgctxt "120_Homeless Man"
msgid "You helped me out down in Purgatory before the Hills project\\r\n"\n"kicked off, then there was that whole snafu with the Dragon Palace."
msgstr "You helped me out down in Purgatory before the Hills project\\r\n"\n"kicked off, then there was that whole snafu with the Dragon Palace."

msgctxt "132_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh. Well, all right then."
msgstr "Huh. Well, all right then."

msgctxt "144_Homeless Man"
msgid "By the way, you're gonna need one of these puppies if you\\r\n"\n"wanna keep going."
msgstr "By the way, you're gonna need one of these puppies if you\\r\n"\n"wanna keep going."

msgctxt "180_Homeless Man"
msgid "This doohickey here'll open any ol' manhole you come across."
msgstr "This doohickey here'll open any ol' manhole you come across."

msgctxt "192_Homeless Man"
msgid "Though some guy came through earlier, pried the freaking\\r\n"\n"thing open with his bare hands. Hardly believed my eyes."
msgstr "Though some guy came through earlier, pried the freaking\\r\n"\n"thing open with his bare hands. Hardly believed my eyes."

msgctxt "204_Homeless Man"
msgid "Heyo, %s-san. Weird of you to be down here, gotta say."
msgstr "Heyo, %s-san. Weird of you to be down here, gotta say."

msgctxt "216_Player"
